org.fxmisc.livedirs

Interface InitiatorTrackingIOFacility<I>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - type of the initiator of I/O actions

    public interface InitiatorTrackingIOFacility<I>
    Simple API for asynchronous file-system operations. The operations are analogous to those of IOFacility, except that every filesystem-changing operation takes an extra argument—the initiator of the change.
